Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.99,0:00:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it’s finally happened. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you’ve found the person \Nof your dreams, and now . . .\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.87,0:00:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re hopelessly in love!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Or are you?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.92,0:00:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you tell if it’s really love?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.13,0:00:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The key is: \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.55,0:00:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You’ve got to learn \Nthe differences between attraction,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,infatuation,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and actual love.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.51,0:00:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Attraction is based on what you see.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.02,0:00:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, how a person looks and acts.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.65,0:00:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is, what you see \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,isn’t always what you get.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.32,0:00:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:00:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,what is infatuation?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.62,0:00:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Infatuation is not only about what you see; \N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it’s about how you feel.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.00,0:01:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You may have romantic feelings. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.42,0:01:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But those feelings can change . . .\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and fast!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.97,0:01:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Infatuation may seem like love. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.01,0:01:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But because it’s based only \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,on how you feel at the moment, . . .\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.01,0:01:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it can just fall apart.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.23,0:01:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do you know if it’s really love? \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.31,0:01:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One that will last?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Real love grows \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.69,0:01:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,when two people are kind,\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.74,0:01:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,hard-working, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.24,0:01:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and share the same spiritual outlook.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,At 1 Corinthians 13:5, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.12,0:01:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the Bible says that real love \N‘doesn’t look for its own interests.’\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.79,0:01:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, \Nthat guy you like so much, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.92,0:01:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,how does he handle money?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he have to drink alcohol \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,to have a good time?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are his goals?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.18,0:01:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he really working toward them? \N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.35,0:02:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is he all talk and no action?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.44,0:02:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about that girl \Nyou just can’t stop thinking about?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are her friends?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.94,0:02:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And how does she treat them?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How does she treat her family?\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s a lot to learn about another person. \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.75,0:02:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes time!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So before you get swept off your feet, \N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,remember:\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Attraction is based on what you see.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Infatuation is based on what you feel.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But real love . . .\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.06,0:03:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is based on what you know.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.70,0:00:11.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,ついに あなたの夢見ていた理想の人が\N現われました\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:15.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,そして—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:19.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,でも 本当に？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.00,0:00:24.63,Default2,,0,0,0,,本当の愛かどうか\Nどうすれば分かるでしょうか？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.63,0:00:26.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,そのかぎは 違いを知ることです\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:35.39,Default2,,0,0,0,,つまり 一目ぼれと……恋と……\N本物の愛の違いです\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.39,0:00:38.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,一目ぼれには\N見ることが関係しています\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.48,0:00:42.48,Default2,,0,0,0,,相手の外見やしぐさに惹かれるのです\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:47.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,でも 見た目と中身は必ずしも\N同じではありません\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:55.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,では 恋とは何ですか？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.24,0:01:01.92,Default2,,0,0,0,,恋には 見ることに加えて\N感じることが関係します\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.92,0:01:04.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,夢見心地になるかもしれません\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:06.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,でも そういう気持ちは\N変わることがあります\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.75,0:01:08.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,しかもすぐに！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.59,0:01:13.68,Default2,,0,0,0,,恋が愛のように思えることがあります\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.68,0:01:16.93,Default2,,0,0,0,,でも それは一時の感情に過ぎないので—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:19.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,簡単に壊れてしまいます\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:26.52,Default2,,0,0,0,,では ずっと続く本当の愛かどうか\Nどうすれば分かるでしょうか？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:31.78,Default2,,0,0,0,,本当の愛は2人が親切を示し合い よく働き—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.78,0:01:34.91,Default2,,0,0,0,,霊的な価値観を共有するときに\N育まれます\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.91,0:01:41.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,聖書のコリント第一 13章5節によると\N本当の愛は“自分の利を求め”ません\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:44.75,Default2,,0,0,0,,例えば あなたの大好きな男の子は—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:48.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,どんなお金の使い方をしますか？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.34,0:01:52.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,お酒がないと楽しめない人ですか？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:55.43,Default2,,0,0,0,,彼の目標は何ですか？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.43,0:01:58.72,Default2,,0,0,0,,その目標に向かって努力していますか？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:02.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,それとも 口先だけでしょうか？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.77,0:02:07.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,あなたの頭から離れない女の子は\Nどうですか？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:11.57,Default2,,0,0,0,,どんな人を友達にしていますか？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.57,0:02:15.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,友達にどう接していますか？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.24,0:02:21.00,Default2,,0,0,0,,家族にどう接していますか？\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:27.04,Default2,,0,0,0,,だれかを本当に知るには\N時間がかかります！\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:33.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,ですから 好きになる前に\N思い出しましょう\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:36.34,Default2,,0,0,0,,一目ぼれは見ること—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:39.97,Default2,,0,0,0,,恋は感じることに左右されます\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:42.47,Default2,,0,0,0,,でも本当の愛は—\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.47,0:03:06.81,Default2,,0,0,0,,知ることが基盤になるのです\N
